    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**《MAHOROBA CAT》**是一款照片冒险游戏，你将在日本著名的旅游景点中旅行。主角受上司委托，为旅游杂志拍摄照片，踏上前往日本各地的旅程。探索精美呈现的体素风景，包括标志性地标、隐藏的秘境和日常场景，努力捕捉完美的瞬间！游戏还提供入住酒店、乘坐火车或巴士等旅行体验，让玩家沉浸在旅程的乐趣中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拿起相机，拍下最佳瞬间！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244270/extras/b100bfcbcf17557c0facdca6b2bf67ec.poster.avif?t=1754108368\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244270/extras/b100bfcbcf17557c0facdca6b2bf67ec.webm?t=1754108368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244270/extras/b100bfcbcf17557c0facdca6b2bf67ec.mp4?t=1754108368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日本各地的旅游景点！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以轻松游览全国各地的旅游景点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244270/extras/49d8a82a820396f6fb81333628af1d37.avif?t=1754108368\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扩展世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >舞台翻转系统让你能够探索微缩世界的每个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244270/extras/3268bdd5ea7c0bf1e6a1c404af646117.poster.avif?t=1754108368\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244270/extras/3268bdd5ea7c0bf1e6a1c404af646117.webm?t=1754108368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244270/extras/3268bdd5ea7c0bf1e6a1c404af646117.mp4?t=1754108368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
